txt.en: You have been recognized as a servant to the master of the Court of Isildur!
Quest of the Court of Isildur -- Tier 1
Service to the master of the Court of Isildur will result in the ability to find your way through the city with less effort.
Complete quests for the benefit of the Court of Isildur!
Grazadhal awaits your return to the Court of Isildur where he will see you rewarded for your service!
You have performed many services for the master of the Court of Isildur.
